1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
♪Let me write the legend♪

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 5=

4
00:00:17,640 --> 00:00:18,440
Come on, Xiaojiu.

5
00:00:19,440 --> 00:00:19,920
Dasheng,

6
00:00:20,480 --> 00:00:21,839
I want to stay a little longer.

7
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:23,039
Just a little while.

8
00:00:23,800 --> 00:00:25,120
Please?

9
00:00:26,199 --> 00:00:26,839
All right, all right.

10
00:00:26,839 --> 00:00:27,719
Whatever you say.

11
00:00:28,039 --> 00:00:28,920
Just a little longer, then.

12
00:00:49,960 --> 00:00:51,640
It worked! It worked!

13
00:00:52,039 --> 00:00:53,079
Looks like the Tianji Armor

14
00:00:53,200 --> 00:00:54,640
is about to choose Mr. Xiao
as its master.

15
00:00:54,920 --> 00:00:56,520
As expected of Nongxiao Pavilion's heir.

16
00:00:56,960 --> 00:00:59,320
To have such good fortune
at such a young age...

17
00:00:59,320 --> 00:01:01,200
He truly deserves it.

18
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:02,159
He just got lucky.

19
00:01:09,239 --> 00:01:11,519
Dasheng, what's wrong?

20
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,879
He's forcing his genuine qi

21
00:01:14,959 --> 00:01:16,519
to merge with the spiritual power
inside the armor.

22
00:01:16,840 --> 00:01:18,400
If he keeps this up,
it could cost him his life.

23
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:26,200
Stop!

24
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:28,359
Forcing the armor on
could get you killed!

25
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:33,959
Oh no! He forced the armor on,

26
00:01:34,079 --> 00:01:35,560
and now it's turning on him.

27
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:38,680
If this continues,
it could cost him his life.

28
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:54,120
What's happening?

29
00:01:55,319 --> 00:01:56,120
What's going on?

30
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:57,920
How did the armor end up on him?

31
00:01:58,079 --> 00:02:00,439
Did the armor choose him as its master?

32
00:02:00,439 --> 00:02:02,280
How is that possible?

33
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:07,280
He actually put it on!

34
00:02:11,159 --> 00:02:14,719
Dasheng, look how beautiful
the Tianji Armor is!

35
00:02:15,479 --> 00:02:17,360
No wonder it's mystic-grade armor.

36
00:02:17,479 --> 00:02:18,319
Do you like it?

37
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:19,800
Of course!

38
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:21,560
I'd only ever heard about it.

39
00:02:21,639 --> 00:02:23,240
This is my first time
seeing it in person.

40
00:02:26,080 --> 00:02:28,000
Thank you for saving my life, sir.

41
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:30,120
It was nothing.

42
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:30,960
Don't mention it.

43
00:02:31,599 --> 00:02:33,879
The Tianji Armor has chosen its master.

44
00:02:33,879 --> 00:02:35,759
It seems he was destined to have it.

45
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:36,960
Young man,

46
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:39,560
you're the one
the armor has been waiting for.

47
00:02:39,599 --> 00:02:41,759
My respects.

48
00:02:42,719 --> 00:02:43,439
Wait!

49
00:02:45,159 --> 00:02:46,360
Mr. Xiao and I were the ones

50
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:48,680
who drained its spiritual power.

51
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:51,120
Why should some penniless nobody
from a no-name sect

52
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:53,000
get the greatest prize under heaven?

53
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,039
I won't accept this!

54
00:02:54,039 --> 00:02:56,120
Exactly! That's right!
Why should he get it?

55
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:56,759
Kun Zhongyu!

56
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:57,400
Why him?

57
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,639
Like it or not,

58
00:02:59,159 --> 00:03:01,240
the armor has already chosen its master.

59
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:03,199
Stop making a scene.

60
00:03:03,199 --> 00:03:04,479
Xiao Ziting,

61
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:06,080
this has nothing to do with you. Move!

62
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:08,240
Have you no shame?

63
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,319
The Daoist already said

64
00:03:09,319 --> 00:03:11,439
it all comes down to fate.

65
00:03:11,719 --> 00:03:12,840
I knew it!

66
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:14,439
You're just jealous.

67
00:03:15,039 --> 00:03:17,400
Maybe that master of yours

68
00:03:17,439 --> 00:03:19,360
used some dirty trick.

69
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:22,879
Otherwise, with his poor talent
and insignificant sect,

70
00:03:22,879 --> 00:03:24,159
how could he possibly deserve

71
00:03:24,159 --> 00:03:26,080
the one-of-a-kind Tianji Armor?

72
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:26,840
What a joke!

73
00:03:27,439 --> 00:03:28,759
Everyone, please be the judge.

74
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,080
I'm taking

75
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:32,000
the Tianji Armor off him today.

76
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,199
I'll expose his trick

77
00:03:33,199 --> 00:03:35,439
and set things right!

78
00:03:35,439 --> 00:03:35,759
That's right!

79
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:36,319
Exactly!

80
00:03:36,439 --> 00:03:37,560
He has a point.

81
00:03:37,879 --> 00:03:38,879
He's right.

82
00:03:38,879 --> 00:03:39,840
That's against the rules.

83
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:40,960
Exactly!

84
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:45,240
You really want to take
this armor off me?

85
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:47,080
Hand it over willingly,

86
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:50,120
and I might spare you.

87
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,520
Then come take it yourself.

88
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:53,400
I promise I won't fight back.

89
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:55,960
Dasheng...

90
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:57,319
Don't worry, Xiaojiu.

91
00:04:01,039 --> 00:04:03,319
(Why is he giving in so easily?)

92
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,759
(Is this a trap?)

93
00:04:04,759 --> 00:04:05,560
What?

94
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:07,080
Scared?

95
00:04:07,199 --> 00:04:11,080
Me? You're the one who should be scared.

96
00:04:11,599 --> 00:04:13,000
In that case,

97
00:04:13,039 --> 00:04:14,639
don't mind if I do.

98
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:38,439
Once the armor chooses its master,

99
00:04:38,519 --> 00:04:40,720
its master gains all
of its spiritual power.

100
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:41,920
The armor will strike back

101
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:43,800
at anyone who tries to take it.

102
00:04:44,079 --> 00:04:45,839
Had Mr. Peng

103
00:04:45,839 --> 00:04:48,160
not held back,

104
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:52,199
his meridians
would've been completely shattered.

105
00:04:52,879 --> 00:04:58,079
Why didn't you say so sooner?

106
00:04:59,279 --> 00:05:00,759
Blessings upon you.

107
00:05:00,759 --> 00:05:02,680
You never asked.

108
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:08,800
(Xuanmiao Temple)

109
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:09,839
(Xuanmiao Temple)
Does anyone else here

110
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:12,600
(Xuanmiao Temple)
want to take this armor off me?

111
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:31,199
Xiaojiu, this armor is yours.

112
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:34,160
Countless heroes would give anything

113
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:35,639
for mystic-grade armor,

114
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,839
and he just handed it to a maid!

115
00:05:37,839 --> 00:05:39,160
This is...

116
00:05:39,160 --> 00:05:40,959
He's unbelievably arrogant!

117
00:05:40,959 --> 00:05:43,279
Exactly! What a waste!

118
00:05:44,399 --> 00:05:46,480
Dasheng, this is too valuable.

119
00:05:46,519 --> 00:05:47,680
I can't accept it.

120
00:05:48,519 --> 00:05:50,240
It's just a piece of armor.

121
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:51,839
Had you not asked me to stay,

122
00:05:51,839 --> 00:05:53,360
it never would've chosen me.

123
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:54,560
So it was yours all along.

124
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:55,399
Take it.

125
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:56,079
But I...

126
00:05:56,079 --> 00:05:56,839
No more buts.

127
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:59,240
This is the first gift
I've ever given you.

128
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:00,319
Please take it.

129
00:06:02,439 --> 00:06:03,519
I love it.

130
00:06:03,519 --> 00:06:04,839
Thank you, Dasheng.

131
00:06:18,199 --> 00:06:19,000
Let's go.

132
00:06:19,839 --> 00:06:20,639
Please wait.

133
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:22,959
What can I do for you?

134
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,360
Please don't misunderstand.

135
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:27,160
You saved my life earlier,

136
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,720
and I haven't thanked you properly.

137
00:06:28,759 --> 00:06:29,519
I've had food and wine prepared

138
00:06:29,519 --> 00:06:31,279
at Liuling Tavern.

139
00:06:31,279 --> 00:06:33,160
I'd be honored if you joined me.

140
00:06:38,079 --> 00:06:40,319
Do you know where
I can get good steamed buns?

141
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:54,600
Dasheng,

142
00:06:54,759 --> 00:06:55,800
you said earlier

143
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:56,680
that you killed

144
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:58,759
the Northern Evil Duo
of the Demon Sect yourself.

145
00:06:58,759 --> 00:07:00,560
Is that really true?

146
00:07:01,279 --> 00:07:02,199
I just got lucky.

147
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:05,120
You took down both of them

148
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:06,800
all by yourself.

149
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:10,040
Dasheng,
your skills are truly impressive.

150
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,040
By the way,

151
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:13,439
you also said

152
00:07:13,439 --> 00:07:13,959
you plan to enter

153
00:07:13,959 --> 00:07:15,759
the Murong family's martial tournament.

154
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:16,879
That's right.

155
00:07:16,879 --> 00:07:17,839
What a coincidence.

156
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:20,160
That's why I came to Gusu too.

157
00:07:25,639 --> 00:07:27,800
You're not after their fortune, are you?

158
00:07:28,199 --> 00:07:29,000
Dasheng!

159
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,879
What kind of man do you think I am?

160
00:07:31,279 --> 00:07:33,560
Nongxiao Pavilion ranks among
the finest in Jiangbei.

161
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:34,959
In family standing or reputation,

162
00:07:34,959 --> 00:07:36,720
we're no less prominent
than the Murongs.

163
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,959
Besides, a man should aim high.

164
00:07:38,959 --> 00:07:40,879
He can't let fame and fortune
stand in his way.

165
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,560
Then why are you going?

166
00:07:43,639 --> 00:07:44,360
Well, Dasheng...

167
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,480
There's something you don't understand.

168
00:07:46,079 --> 00:07:48,160
I come from a prestigious martial family

169
00:07:48,279 --> 00:07:49,199
and earned the title

170
00:07:49,199 --> 00:07:51,120
of Mr. Charming at a young age.

171
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:53,319
But it's all just for show.

172
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:55,759
Ever since I set out on my own,

173
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:57,560
rumors have followed me
throughout the martial world.

174
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:58,680
Everyone says I've only gotten this far

175
00:07:58,759 --> 00:08:00,720
because of my father's name.

176
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:01,600
To this day...

177
00:08:04,959 --> 00:08:05,920
I get it.

178
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:08,639
You want to prove yourself
at the martial tournament

179
00:08:08,759 --> 00:08:11,839
and shut your critics up, right?

180
00:08:15,439 --> 00:08:16,480
What an appetite!

181
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:17,680
Dasheng,

182
00:08:17,839 --> 00:08:19,360
you really do understand me.

183
00:08:20,079 --> 00:08:21,920
Since we're both far from home,

184
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,639
why don't we go together?

185
00:08:23,639 --> 00:08:24,879
Of course.

186
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:26,959
And thanks for the meal.

187
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,160
Honestly,

188
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,279
I haven't eaten this much

189
00:08:30,279 --> 00:08:33,399
since I came down the mountain.

190
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,279
Dasheng.

191
00:08:43,279 --> 00:08:44,080
Here you are.

192
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:46,639
Take it.

193
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:50,279
All of this is for me?

194
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:52,759
It's yours, if you'll accept it.

195
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:53,919
No, Ziting,

196
00:08:53,919 --> 00:08:54,960
this is too much.

197
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:56,639
We're both men of the martial world.

198
00:08:56,639 --> 00:08:58,480
You don't have to be so polite.

199
00:08:58,480 --> 00:09:00,279
Besides, a man needs some silver

200
00:09:00,279 --> 00:09:02,000
when he's out in the world.

201
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:03,159
Even if you don't need it,

202
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:04,360
Xiaojiu might.

203
00:09:04,879 --> 00:09:05,679
Take it.

204
00:09:10,759 --> 00:09:11,279
Thank you.

205
00:09:12,399 --> 00:09:14,200
No need to thank me. We're friends.

206
00:09:14,279 --> 00:09:15,639
Whenever you need my help,

207
00:09:15,639 --> 00:09:16,600
just say the word.

208
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:19,480
Ziting,

209
00:09:23,120 --> 00:09:24,399
since I came down the mountain,
you're the first person

210
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:27,720
who's wanted to be my friend.

211
00:09:39,679 --> 00:09:41,399
Xiaojiu has been out
shopping for jewelry for so long.

212
00:09:41,399 --> 00:09:42,519
Why isn't she back yet?

213
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:44,720
There's so much

214
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:45,639
to choose from in Gusu.

215
00:09:45,919 --> 00:09:47,639
Maybe she can't decide what to buy.

216
00:09:49,039 --> 00:09:49,559
That makes sense.

217
00:10:05,639 --> 00:10:06,480
Sir,

218
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:09,240
was that young lady named Fang

219
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,399
your friend?

220
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:11,480
What happened to her?

221
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:14,080
The Sihai Gang took her.

222
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:15,440
They asked me to deliver a message.

223
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:17,600
You must go alone to Wuchi Alley
if you want her back.

224
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:18,600
The Sihai Gang?

225
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:20,200
They're a local gang in Gusu.

226
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:21,039
They do whatever they want around here

227
00:10:21,039 --> 00:10:21,919
and are hard to deal with.

228
00:10:23,879 --> 00:10:24,200
Dasheng...

229
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:24,720
Wuchi Alley...

230
00:10:24,759 --> 00:10:25,240
Dasheng!

231
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:36,080
Well, beautiful,

232
00:10:36,799 --> 00:10:39,240
you woke up at just the right time.

233
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:43,639
Who are you? Where am I?

234
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:47,679
(Wang Yang, Leader of the Sihai Gang)
Here's the truth.

235
00:10:47,679 --> 00:10:49,279
(Wang Yang, Leader of the Sihai Gang)
Someone hired me

236
00:10:49,279 --> 00:10:51,320
to teach the guy you were with a lesson.

237
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:52,399
But there were too many people

238
00:10:52,399 --> 00:10:54,639
watching on the street,

239
00:10:54,759 --> 00:10:56,120
so we grabbed you

240
00:10:56,240 --> 00:10:57,799
to lure him here.

241
00:10:58,159 --> 00:11:02,399
But a beauty like you...

242
00:11:04,799 --> 00:11:06,039
What a shame to let you go to waste.

243
00:11:06,039 --> 00:11:07,840
What a shame!

244
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:11,639
You wretched woman!

245
00:11:11,639 --> 00:11:12,600
How dare you kick me?

246
00:11:14,399 --> 00:11:15,879
I'll show you what happens

247
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:18,639
when you cross me!

248
00:11:23,399 --> 00:11:24,799
Mmm, you smell nice.

249
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:28,600
(Keep me happy, sweetheart.)

250
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:34,919
Let me go!

251
00:11:42,519 --> 00:11:43,559
Where's Xiaojiu?

252
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:46,639
You mean that loose woman?

253
00:11:46,679 --> 00:11:49,360
I heard her screaming in there
a minute ago.

254
00:11:49,399 --> 00:11:50,679
But by now,

255
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:53,679
she's probably having too much fun
to make a sound.

256
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:55,360
You're asking for it.

257
00:12:17,039 --> 00:12:17,720
Xiaojiu!

258
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:23,120
Dasheng!

259
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:29,799
Are you hurt?

260
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:44,039
Changsheng?

261
00:12:53,140 --> 00:12:53,620
♪Come on♪

262
00:12:57,140 --> 00:12:58,820
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

263
00:13:00,780 --> 00:13:03,740
♪In worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust♪

264
00:13:04,020 --> 00:13:06,940
♪Among the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?♪

265
00:13:07,180 --> 00:13:10,020
♪They say my birth
has already decided my path♪

266
00:13:10,420 --> 00:13:13,020
♪But I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth♪

267
00:13:13,540 --> 00:13:16,500
♪With one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms♪

268
00:13:16,740 --> 00:13:19,740
♪Covered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless♪

269
00:13:19,900 --> 00:13:22,820
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

270
00:13:22,980 --> 00:13:25,740
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

271
00:13:26,300 --> 00:13:29,620
♪Listen, this heartbeat echoes♪

272
00:13:29,660 --> 00:13:32,660
♪Fate is nothing but a net♪

273
00:13:32,700 --> 00:13:38,340
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

274
00:13:38,740 --> 00:13:40,780
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

275
00:13:41,340 --> 00:13:43,860
♪I don't believe
anyone is born above another♪

276
00:13:44,580 --> 00:13:46,980
♪Even this mortal body
dares to fight back♪

277
00:13:47,100 --> 00:13:50,780
♪I'll step on fate and grow beyond it♪

278
00:13:51,380 --> 00:13:53,500
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

279
00:13:54,420 --> 00:13:56,540
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

280
00:13:56,700 --> 00:13:59,980
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

281
00:14:00,020 --> 00:14:04,300
♪I am my own king♪

282
00:14:17,380 --> 00:14:18,940
♪I emerge into the world♪

283
00:14:18,940 --> 00:14:20,700
♪Unknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world♪

284
00:14:20,700 --> 00:14:22,060
♪My pride is my trump card♪

285
00:14:22,060 --> 00:14:23,860
♪Even if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield♪

286
00:14:23,860 --> 00:14:25,260
♪Born with a gift, I won't give in♪

287
00:14:25,260 --> 00:14:27,020
♪Against heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise♪

288
00:14:27,020 --> 00:14:28,540
♪A sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain♪

289
00:14:28,540 --> 00:14:30,260
♪I dare to break every rule♪

290
00:14:30,260 --> 00:14:31,580
♪I see through
the masks of human hearts♪

291
00:14:31,580 --> 00:14:33,420
♪Famous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise♪

292
00:14:33,420 --> 00:14:34,660
♪They kneel and beg for fame♪

293
00:14:34,660 --> 00:14:36,900
♪I stand and fight for my dignity♪

294
00:14:36,900 --> 00:14:38,420
♪Facing powerful foes, I will not bow♪

295
00:14:38,420 --> 00:14:40,020
♪With my blade in hand,
I decide what is right♪

296
00:14:40,020 --> 00:14:41,620
♪Stand for justice and never step back♪

297
00:14:41,620 --> 00:14:43,340
♪Even if the whole world
stands against me♪

298
00:14:43,340 --> 00:14:45,060
♪Untamed,
frost has carved me to the bone♪

299
00:14:45,060 --> 00:14:46,420
♪Only then do I become more like myself♪

300
00:14:46,420 --> 00:14:48,060
♪Fight, this life of mine is unyielding♪

301
00:14:48,060 --> 00:14:49,540
♪No matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it♪

302
00:14:49,540 --> 00:14:51,260
♪For love, I do not fight for the world♪

303
00:14:51,260 --> 00:14:52,860
♪I only want
to protect her for a lifetime♪

304
00:14:52,860 --> 00:14:54,420
♪Carefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay♪

305
00:14:54,420 --> 00:14:58,740
♪Now I know all things can be overcome♪

306
00:14:58,740 --> 00:15:00,900
♪I raise my blade and change my fate♪

307
00:15:00,900 --> 00:15:03,500
♪Let me write the legend♪

308
00:15:08,380 --> 00:15:10,940
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

309
00:15:10,940 --> 00:15:14,260
♪Win or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me♪

310
00:15:14,260 --> 00:15:16,740
♪Even if I fall, I will still shine♪

311
00:15:16,740 --> 00:15:20,820
♪Let my name
be carved into the vast world♪

312
00:15:21,180 --> 00:15:23,780
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

313
00:15:23,900 --> 00:15:26,260
♪If this world refuses to forgive me♪

314
00:15:26,260 --> 00:15:29,300
♪Then I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance♪

315
00:15:29,300 --> 00:15:34,340
♪And trade it for a new dawn♪
